{"id":59184,"date":"2024-09-16T16:51:00","date_gmt":"2024-09-16T11:21:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=59184"},"modified":"2024-09-18T21:53:05","modified_gmt":"2024-09-18T16:23:05","slug":"corner-wardrobe-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/corner-wardrobe-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Corner Wardrobe Design: The Ultimate Space-Saving Solution for Bedrooms"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Transform small spaces with stylish corner wardrobe designs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Today, space has become a high-value commodity in real estate. People are ready to pay big bucks for smart home solutions and modular furniture to optimise every single inch of square footage. When it comes to bedrooms, one of the easiest ways to save some precious floor space is by building corner wardrobe units that are either built-in or flush to the wall. With smart storage mechanisms, drawers, and attractive shutters, corner wardrobes can declutter space, make it more functional, and add immense value to the property.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s look into the various benefits of corner wardrobes, design ideas, and tips on how to make the most out of this often-overlooked item.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Top Benefits of Having Corner Wardrobes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Space Optimisation with Best Corner Wardrobe Design<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Corner wardrobes are most interior designers\u2019 secret tool to utilise the often-unused corners of a room. They not only save a ton of floor space but also allow better movement. For apartments with smaller rooms, the small corner wardrobe design is a game-changer for maximising storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add More Storage Through L-shaped Corner Wardrobe<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When every inch of space counts, a built-in corner wardrobe makes excellent use of wall space. It offers ample storage, especially when designed with smart shelves and unique compartments. That\u2019s not all; you can easily customise a corner wardrobe with shelves to create a floating vanity unit that keeps all the beauty essentials neatly organised and handy, which would be otherwise impossible to fit in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">small bedrooms<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Increase Aesthetic Appeal with Small Corner Wardrobe Design\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Today, homeowners are looking for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/multi-purpose-furniture-ideas\/\">multipurpose furniture<\/a> that is equally stylish to fit their changing aesthetic needs. So, modern corner wardrobe designs are evaluated not only by their functionality but also by their aesthetic appeal. From sleek, minimalist styles to more intricate designs, there&#8217;s a corner wardrobe design to suit every taste. Whether you&#8217;re looking for a corner L-shaped wardrobe design or a corner wardrobe with a study table, these wardrobes now seamlessly blend style with utility.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Customisation with Modern Corner Wardrobe Design<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best advantages of investing in a modular corner wardrobe is the freedom to customise it according to your needs. You can choose the size, material, internal layout, and outer look. This ensures that your wardrobe meets all your storage needs while complementing your bedroom&#8217;s d\u00e9cor. For instance, a corner wardrobe with a dressing table or an L-corner wardrobe is trendy among many urban homeowners.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214514\/corner-wardrobe-benefits.jpg\" alt=\"A corner wardrobe designed to optimise space, provide enhanced storage, and offer customisable aesthetics for any room\" class=\"wp-image-59186\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214514\/corner-wardrobe-benefits.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214514\/corner-wardrobe-benefits-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214514\/corner-wardrobe-benefits-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214514\/corner-wardrobe-benefits-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Create a styling nook with an L-corner wardrobe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Explore efficient and affordable wardrobe designs\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/09125247\/explore-efficient-and-affordable-wardrobe-designs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Design Ideas for Corner Wardrobes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sliding Door Corner Wardrobe Ideas for Small Bedrooms<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A sliding-door corner wardrobe becomes the most sensible choice when space comes with a premium price tag. Sliding doors eliminate the need for additional space to open, making them ideal for small bedrooms. Such wardrobes exude style and are space-efficient.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214644\/sliding-door-corner-wardrobe-ideas-for-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Corner wardrobe ideas for small bedroom with sliding doors that exude style and are space-efficient\" class=\"wp-image-59193\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214644\/sliding-door-corner-wardrobe-ideas-for-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214644\/sliding-door-corner-wardrobe-ideas-for-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214644\/sliding-door-corner-wardrobe-ideas-for-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214644\/sliding-door-corner-wardrobe-ideas-for-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Sliding doors are a must in compact spaces<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sleek Glass Front Small Corner Wardrobe Design<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Glass-front corner wardrobes, made of transparent or frosted glass, add a touch of elegance to any room. The glass makes the space look larger and allows you to show off your clothing collection. This type of wardrobe is particularly effective in compact homes, where enhancing the visual space is key.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214501\/corner-l-shaped-wardrobe-design-glass-front.jpg\" alt=\"A corner l-shaped wardrobe design with a frosted glass front creates an illusion of space in compact homes\" class=\"wp-image-59185\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214501\/corner-l-shaped-wardrobe-design-glass-front.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214501\/corner-l-shaped-wardrobe-design-glass-front-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214501\/corner-l-shaped-wardrobe-design-glass-front-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214501\/corner-l-shaped-wardrobe-design-glass-front-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Frosted glass enhances the room\u2019s visual space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Celeb-like Walk-In Modern Corner Wardrobe Design<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have more space to spare, a walk-in corner wardrobe\/closet is the ultimate idea to add a luxe feel and functionality at the same time. Separate this space with a sliding glass door, and you will have your private dressing area &#8211; just like in the movies and celebs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214656\/walk-in-corner-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Brown walk-in corner wardrobe featuring a sliding glass door entrance\" class=\"wp-image-59194\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214656\/walk-in-corner-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214656\/walk-in-corner-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214656\/walk-in-corner-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214656\/walk-in-corner-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Teak-wood wardrobe looks stylish<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stunning Mirrored Corner Wardrobe Designs<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mirrored corner wardrobes are a fantastic option for smaller bedrooms. If placed opposite a window, the mirrors reflect light, making the room feel brighter and more spacious. This type of bedroom corner wardrobe is ideal for those looking to combine multifunctionality with style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214538\/corner-wardrobe-ideas-with-mirror.jpg\" alt=\"A corner wardrobe with attached mirrors on doors\" class=\"wp-image-59188\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214538\/corner-wardrobe-ideas-with-mirror.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214538\/corner-wardrobe-ideas-with-mirror-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214538\/corner-wardrobe-ideas-with-mirror-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214538\/corner-wardrobe-ideas-with-mirror-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mirrors and windows create a bright space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Minimalist Corner Wardrobe With Shelves<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For a more open and minimalist look, consider an open-shelving corner wardrobe. This design offers easy access to your belongings while maintaining a clean, uncluttered appearance. It&#8217;s a popular choice for those who prefer a modern, airy feel in their bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214602\/corner-wardrobe-with-shelves.jpg\" alt=\"Corner wardrobe with shelves for organised storage\" class=\"wp-image-59190\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214602\/corner-wardrobe-with-shelves.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214602\/corner-wardrobe-with-shelves-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214602\/corner-wardrobe-with-shelves-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214602\/corner-wardrobe-with-shelves-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Open-shelving combines easy access with a minimalist design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corner Wardrobe Design With Study Table<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Why limit yourself to a corner wardrobe when you can attach a study table to it? This breaks the monotonous layout and infuses a unique element into the room. The small space employs white colour to appear bigger than it is. The wardrobe and the study table add functionality and efficiency, while the red bedspread adds a much-needed pop of colour.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214615\/corner-wardrobe-with-study-table.jpg\" alt=\"White corner wardrobe with study table optimises space\" class=\"wp-image-59191\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214615\/corner-wardrobe-with-study-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214615\/corner-wardrobe-with-study-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214615\/corner-wardrobe-with-study-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214615\/corner-wardrobe-with-study-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Floor-to-ceiling corner wardrobe with a top shelf for storing rarely used items<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corner Wardrobe With Dressing Table<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Customising your wardrobe with specific compartments for shoes, accessories, and other items can significantly enhance its functionality. This level of customisation ensures that your corner wardrobe meets all your storage needs. A popular trend is incorporating a dressing table with the wardrobe design.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214551\/corner-wardrobe-with-dressing-table.jpg\" alt=\"Corner wardrobe with dressing table enhancing functionality\" class=\"wp-image-59189\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214551\/corner-wardrobe-with-dressing-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214551\/corner-wardrobe-with-dressing-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214551\/corner-wardrobe-with-dressing-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214551\/corner-wardrobe-with-dressing-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A gorgeous, expansive wardrobe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips for Optimising Your Corner Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Incorporate Lighting in Modern Corner Wardrobe Design<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Good lighting is essential in a wardrobe. Consider adding LED strip lights or spotlights inside your wardrobe to ensure all areas are well-lit. This will make it easier to find your belongings and add a touch of luxury to your wardrobe space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Choose the Right Material&nbsp;<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The material you choose for your wardrobe can significantly impact its durability and appearance. Opt for materials complementing your room&#8217;s overall design while offering long-lasting durability. Whether it&#8217;s wood, glass, or a combination, the right material can elevate the look of your bedroom furniture corner wardrobes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Use Vertical Space Efficiently<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>When designing your corner wardrobe, make sure to utilise the vertical space. Adding shelves or hanging racks from floor to ceiling can significantly increase your storage capacity. This is especially important in corner wardrobe designs for small bedrooms, where every bit of space matters.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214630\/modern-corner-wardrobe-design-tips.jpg\" alt=\"Modern corner wardrobe design with customised LED lightings\" class=\"wp-image-59192\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214630\/modern-corner-wardrobe-design-tips.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214630\/modern-corner-wardrobe-design-tips-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214630\/modern-corner-wardrobe-design-tips-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/18214630\/modern-corner-wardrobe-design-tips-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Give your wardrobe a premium look with customisable LED lights<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The corner wardrobe design is a smart choice for any compact bedroom, offering both practicality and aesthetic appeal. Whether you are looking to maximise the space or simply want to add a modern touch to your bedroom, this type<strong> <\/strong>of wardrobe design could be the perfect addition.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like this article? Check out our blog section for more such<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/\"> wardrobe design ideas<\/a>. If you want to transform your bedroom or home into a dreamy abode,<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\"> book a free consultation<\/a> with us today!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ On Corner Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. What are the advantages of using a corner wardrobe in a bedroom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Maximises Space: <\/strong>Corner wardrobes efficiently use unused corners, freeing up valuable floor space and improving room flow, especially in smaller bedrooms.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Enhances Storage:<\/strong> They provide ample storage with smart shelving and compartments and can be customised to include features like a floating vanity unit.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Increases Aesthetic Appeal: <\/strong>Modern corner wardrobe designs blend functionality with style, offering sleek, minimalist or intricate designs that suit any d\u00e9cor.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Offers Customisation:<\/strong> Modular corner wardrobes can be tailored in size, material, and layout to meet specific storage needs while complementing the bedroom&#8217;s design.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. How do I choose the right size of a corner wardrobe for my bedroom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To choose the right size of a corner wardrobe, measure the available corner space carefully, considering both height and width. Ensure the wardrobe doesn&#8217;t obstruct movement or other furniture. Opt for a design that maximises storage while fitting seamlessly within the dimensions of your room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Can a corner wardrobe be customised to suit my specific storage needs?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, a corner wardrobe can be fully customised to suit your specific storage needs. You can choose the size, material, internal layout, and additional features to ensure it perfectly fits your space and style preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. How can I ensure proper organisation within a corner wardrobe?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Customise your corner wardrobe with specific compartments for shoes, accessories, and other items to ensure proper organisation and maximise functionality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. Are there any specific maintenance tips for corner wardrobes?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Regularly dust and clean your corner wardrobe, avoid overloading shelves, and occasionally lubricate doors and hinges to ensure smooth operation.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/u